1. Navigated into the repository: alx-intermediate-frontend
2. Created directory: 0x03-sass_scss
3. Installed NVM using:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
4. Restarted the terminal and installed Node.js version 20.16 using:
   nvm install 20.16
5. Set the node version using:
   nvm use 20.16
6. Installed the latest stable version of SASS using:
   npm install sass
